# ✅ Mubra AI - Complete Deployment Checklist

## 📋 Pre-Launch Checklist

### Phase 1: Preparation (15 minutes)

- [ ] Download all files from GitHub or output folder
- [ ] Files downloaded:
  - [ ] mubra-chemistry-app.html
  - [ ] README.md
  - [ ] QUICKSTART.md
  - [ ] DESIGN-SPECIFICATIONS.md
- [ ] Create a folder called `mubra-chemistry`
- [ ] Place all files in this folder

### Phase 2: API Configuration (5 minutes)

- [ ] Visit https://aistudio.google.com
- [ ] Click "Get API key"
- [ ] Select "Create API key in new project"
- [ ] Copy the API key shown
- [ ] Open `mubra-chemistry-app.html` in text editor
- [ ] Find line: `GEMINI_API_KEY: 'YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_HERE',`
- [ ] Replace with your actual key (keep quotes)
- [ ] Save the file (Ctrl+S / Cmd+S)

**Example:**
```javascript
// Before
GEMINI_API_KEY: 'YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_HERE',

// After
GEMINI_API_KEY: 'AIzaSyD_abc123XYZ789_your_real_key_here',
```

### Phase 3: Local Testing (10 minutes)

**Test 1: File Opens**
- [ ] Double-click `mubra-chemistry-app.html`
- [ ] App opens in default browser
- [ ] No error messages in console (F12)

**Test 2: Visual Verification**
- [ ] Logo "Mubra AI 8.v1" visible in sidebar
- [ ] Navy blue (#001F3F) and gold (#D4AF37) colors present
- [ ] Sidebar shows lessons: Organic, Inorganic, Physical
- [ ] Sidebar shows years: 1985-2025
- [ ] Header displays welcome message
- [ ] Chat window shows welcome container
- [ ] Input field visible at bottom

**Test 3: Interactivity**
- [ ] Click "Organic Chemistry" lesson
  - [ ] Header updates to "Organic Chemistry"
  - [ ] Sidebar item highlighted
  - [ ] Chat shows welcome screen
- [ ] Click a year (e.g., 2020)
  - [ ] Header updates to "2020"
  - [ ] Year highlighted in sidebar
  - [ ] Chat shows welcome screen

**Test 4: Chat Functionality**
- [ ] Type message: "Hello, test message"
- [ ] Click send button (📤) or press Shift+Enter
- [ ] User message appears in blue on right
- [ ] Typing indicator appears (three dots)
- [ ] Wait for AI response (1-3 seconds)
- [ ] AI response appears in white with gold border
- [ ] Message auto-scrolls to bottom
- [ ] Input field clears

**Test 5: Chemistry Formulas**
- [ ] Ask: "What is the formula for sulfuric acid?"
- [ ] Look for $H_2SO_4$ in response
- [ ] Verify formula renders properly (not raw text)
- [ ] Ask about equilibrium: "Explain Kp"
- [ ] Verify $K_p$ renders correctly

**Test 6: Mobile Responsive**
- [ ] Press F12 to open DevTools
- [ ] Click device toolbar (toggle responsive design)
- [ ] Test iPhone SE (375x667)
  - [ ] Sidebar is horizontal
  - [ ] Chat width is ~90%
  - [ ] Input area is compact
  - [ ] No horizontal scroll
- [ ] Test iPad (768x1024)
  - [ ] Sidebar narrower but visible
  - [ ] Chat is centered
  - [ ] Layout looks good
- [ ] Test Desktop (1920x1080)
  - [ ] Sidebar full width (280px)
  - [ ] Chat window centered
  - [ ] Optimal spacing

**Test 7: Sinhala Support**
- [ ] Sidebar headers show: "පාඩම්" and "📋 Past Papers"
- [ ] Text renders clearly (no ???)
- [ ] Sinhala text is readable

### Phase 4: Documentation Review (5 minutes)

- [ ] README.md contents understood
  - [ ] Feature overview read
  - [ ] Technology stack confirmed
  - [ ] Setup instructions clear
- [ ] QUICKSTART.md reviewed
  - [ ] Quick start steps make sense
  - [ ] Example questions noted
