## 📞 Troubleshooting During Deployment

### "GitHub Pages shows 404"
- [ ] Wait 1-2 minutes for deployment
- [ ] Refresh the page
- [ ] Check URL is exactly correct
- [ ] Verify repository is Public

### "App loads but API doesn't work"
- [ ] Check API key is configured correctly
- [ ] Verify no extra spaces in key
- [ ] Check F12 console for error messages
- [ ] Verify internet connection
- [ ] Try in incognito/private window

### "Formulas show as raw text"
- [ ] Check internet connection
- [ ] KaTeX loads from CDN
- [ ] Refresh the page
- [ ] Try different browser

### "Sinhala text shows as ???"
- [ ] Check file is saved as UTF-8
- [ ] Check HTML has `<meta charset="UTF-8">`
- [ ] Try different browser
- [ ] Update browser

